@startuml sequence-booking-penitipan
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram — Booking Penitipan / Pet Hotel (End-to-End)

actor Pelanggan
actor "Staff / Owner" as Staff
participant "Aplikasi Web" as App
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB

== Ajukan Penitipan ==

Pelanggan -> App : Buka menu Penitipan
App -> API : GET /kucing?eligible_pet_hotel=true
API -> DB : SELECT kucing + COUNT riwayat_vaksin\nWHERE jenis & tanggal terisi
DB --> API : Daftar kucing eligible / belum eligible
API --> App : Data kucing
App --> Pelanggan : Dropdown kucing (dengan status eligible)

Pelanggan -> App : Pilih kucing
App -> API : GET /kucing/{id}/riwayat-vaksin
API -> DB : SELECT riwayat_vaksin
DB --> API : Riwayat vaksin
API --> App : Ringkasan vaksin (read-only)
App --> Pelanggan : Tampilkan riwayat vaksin

alt Riwayat vaksin < 1 entri lengkap
  App --> Pelanggan : Form ditolak — lengkapi vaksin di "Kucing Saya"
else Vaksin memenuhi syarat
  Pelanggan -> App : Isi check-in, check-out,\ncatatan makan, opsi pengantaran
  App -> API : POST /penitipan/estimasi-biaya
  API -> API : Hitung subtotal, promo 10%\n(durasi >7 hari & belum pernah pakai)
  API -> API : Hitung biaya antar-jemput (jika ada)
  API --> App : Ringkasan biaya
  App --> Pelanggan : Tampilkan estimasi harga

  Pelanggan -> App : Submit penitipan
  App -> API : POST /booking/penitipan
  API -> DB : INSERT booking_penitipan\nstatus = MENUNGGU_KONFIRMASI
  API -> DB : INSERT transaksi (draft)
  DB --> API : OK
  API --> App : 201 Created
  App --> Pelanggan : Penitipan diajukan
end

== Konfirmasi Staff ==

Staff -> App : Buka detail booking penitipan
App -> API : GET /internal/booking/penitipan/{id}
API -> DB : SELECT booking + kucing + riwayat_vaksin
DB --> API : Detail booking
API --> App : Data lengkap
App --> Staff : Tampilkan detail + vaksin (read-only)

alt Vaksin tidak memenuhi syarat
  Staff -> App : Tolak booking
  App -> API : PATCH .../tolak
  API -> DB : UPDATE status = DIBATALKAN
  API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi BOOKING_DITOLAK
  App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi ditolak
else Vaksin OK & staff konfirmasi
  Staff -> App : Konfirmasi penitipan
  App -> API : PATCH .../konfirmasi
  API -> DB : UPDATE status = MENUNGGU_PEMBAYARAN
  API -> DB : UPDATE transaksi.batas_waktu_bayar
  API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi
  App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi tagihan
end

== Pembayaran ==

Pelanggan -> App : Upload bukti transfer
App -> API : POST /transaksi/{id}/bukti-transfer
API -> DB : INSERT bukti_transfer\nstatus = MENUNGGU_VERIFIKASI_BUKTI
App --> Pelanggan : Menunggu verifikasi

Staff -> App : Setujui bukti transfer
App -> API : PATCH /internal/bukti-transfer/{id}/setujui
API -> DB : UPDATE transaksi = LUNAS
API -> DB : UPDATE booking = TERKONFIRMASI
opt Promo dipakai
  API -> DB : UPDATE pelanggan.pernah_pakai_promo_penitipan = true
end
API -> DB : INSERT invoice
App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi lunas + invoice

== Check-in → Monitoring → Check-out ==

Staff -> App : Update status → CHECK_IN
App -> API : PATCH .../status (CHECK_IN)
API -> DB : UPDATE status
Staff -> App : Update status → SEDANG_DITITIPKAN
App -> API : PATCH .../status (SEDANG_DITITIPKAN)
API -> DB : UPDATE status

loop Setiap hari penitipan
  Staff -> App : Input monitoring harian\n(foto, makan, kondisi, aktivitas)
  App -> API : POST /internal/monitoring-penitipan
  API -> DB : INSERT monitoring_penitipan
  API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi MONITORING_PENITIPAN
  App --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi update monitoring
end

Staff -> App : Update status → CHECK_OUT
App -> API : PATCH .../status (CHECK_OUT)
API -> DB : UPDATE status
App --> Pelanggan : Penitipan selesai

@enduml
